2005-09-29 13:12  rkowen

	* utility.c, testsuite/modules.50-cmds/075-alias.exp,
	testsuite/modules.50-cmds/077-alias-undo.exp: * Added or Fine-tuned
	the --enable-shell-funcs, --enable-shell-alias	 and
	--enable-shell-eval configure options.	The configure script   will
	test for the existence of the first two properties in /bin/sh  
	where the options can override the tested values.  Made the  
	associated tests conditional on the existence of these properties.

