2005-04-08 02:29  sirdude

	* tcl/modulecmd.tcl: 
	
	Fix up module init(cmds) I made them behave like the c versions    
	    example before the initadd added a module to every module load
	line	 now it just does the first.
	
	I have a ~/.modules directory and before this caused the init(cmds)
	to fail.
	
	Also made it so it only changes one file not all . files it goes
	through.
	
	Kent

