	* tcl/init/: bash.in, csh.in, ksh.in, perl.in, python.in, sh.in,
	tcsh.in, zsh.in: 
	tcl version of modules now looks at environment var TCLSH if it
	exits and uses that first.
	
	Suggested by David Astrom.
	
