2004-01-15 22:28  sirdude

	* tcl/Makefile, testsuite/config/unix.exp: 
	
	Made it so that the testsuite works with the tcl version of
	modules.  Current stats for the tcl version are: # of expected
	passes		  146 # of unexpected failures	      376
	
	Not too shabby, I'm guessing it will be fairly straight forward to
	increase this by quite a bit.
	
	Kent

2004-01-15 07:53  sirdude

	* tcl/init/: bash.in, csh.in, ksh.in, perl.in, python.in, sh.in,
	tcsh.in, zsh.in: 
	
	Modified the tcl init files so that they try to find tclsh, this
	should make them quite a bit faster assuming they find it.  (This
	way it locates the shell just once instead of for every single
	command.)
	
	Kent

2004-01-15 07:49  sirdude

	* tcl/modulecmd.tcl: 
	
