2002-03-09 23:22  rkowen

	* ModuleCmd_Avail.c: Due to Mark Lakata.  Fixed bug in mkdirnm.
	There was a check to see if the dir eq ".", but was done using a
	char comparison, not string comparison. Caused severe problems if
	dir was "..", since only first character was used.

