2001-07-25 21:59  rkowen

	* cmdPath.c, version.c, testsuite/modulefiles/info/isloaded,
	testsuite/modulefiles/loc_dv1/1.0,
	testsuite/modulefiles/loc_dv1/2.0,
	testsuite/modules.50-cmds/088-info-isloaded.exp,
	testsuite/modules.50-cmds/170-swap.exp: * Fixed "module swap" to
	put the substituted module in the   same path location as the old. 
	Also added a number of tests   for this feature.    (Bug was
	pointed out by Leo Butler <lbutler@brocade.com>)  * Added tests for
	the "is-loaded" modulefile command introduced	back in 3.0.8-rko.

